\c 9
\s UJesu uvula amehlo esiphofu
\p
\v 1 Wathi esedlula wabona umuntu oyisiphofu kusukela ekuzalweni.
\v 2 Abafundi bakhe basebembuza bathi: \w Rabi\w**\x + 1.38.\x*, ngubani owonayo\x + 9.34.\x*, lo kumbe abazali bakhe, aze azalwe eyisiphofu\x + Eks. 20.5.\x*?
\v 3 UJesu waphendula \add wathi\add*: Konanga lo loba abazali bakhe; kodwa ukuze kubonakaliswe imisebenzi kaNkulunkulu kuye\x + 11.4.\x*.
\v 4 Kufanele ngisebenze imisebenzi yongithumileyo\x + 4.34. 5.19,36. 17.4.\x* kusesemini\x + 11.9. 12.35. Roma 13.12.\x*; ubusuku buyeza, lapho okungekho olakho ukusebenza khona.
\v 5 Ngisekhona emhlabeni, ngiyikukhanya komhlaba\x + 1.4,9.\x*.
\v 6 Esetshilo lezizinto, wakhafulela emhlabathini, wenza udaka ngamathe, waninda loludaka emehlweni esiphofu\x + Mark. 7.33. 8.23. 2 Kho. 2.21. Mat. 20.34.\x*,
\v 7 wasesithi kuso: Hamba uyegeza echibini leSilowama\x + Neh. 3.15.\x* (okuphendulelwa \add ngokuthi\add*, oThunyiweyo). Ngakho sahamba sageza, sabuya sesibona\x + 11.37. 2 Kho. 5.10,14.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Ngakho abakhelene laso lalabo ababesibonile ngaphambili ukuthi sasiyisiphofu\x + Mat. 25.24.\x*, bathi: Kayisuye yini lo owayehlezi ephanza\x + Seb. 3.2,10.\x*?
\v 9 Abanye bathi: Lo nguye; kodwa abanye \add bathi\add*: Unjengaye. Yena wathi: Ngingu\add ye\add*.
\v 10 Ngakho bathi kuye: Avulwe njani amehlo akho?
\v 11 Yena waphendula wathi: Umuntu othiwa nguJesu wenze udaka, waninda amehlo ami, wathi kimi: Hamba uye echibini leSilowama, ugeze. Njalo ngahamba ngageza, ngabuye ngabona\x + 9.6,7.\x*.
\v 12 Ngakho bathi kuye: Ungaphi yena? Wathi: Kangazi.
\p
\v 13 Basebemletha kubaFarisi, lowo owayekade eyisiphofu.
\v 14 Njalo kwakulisabatha mhla uJesu esenza udaka, evula amehlo akhe\x + 5.9.\x*.
\v 15 AbaFarisi labo basebembuza futhi, ukuthi wemukele njani ukubona. Wasesithi kubo: Ufake udaka emehlweni ami, ngasengigeza, sengibona\x + 9.10.\x*.
\v 16 Ngakho abanye babaFarisi bathi: Lumuntu kaveli kuNkulunkulu\x + 9.33. 6.46.\x*, ngoba kagcini isabatha\x + Mat. 12.10.\x*. Abanye bathi\x + 3.2. 19.38,39.\x*: Umuntu oyisoni angazenza njani izibonakaliso ezinje\x + 9.33.\x*? Kwasekusiba khona ukwehlukana phakathi kwabo\x + 7.43.\x*.
\v 17 Baphinda bathi kuso isiphofu: Wena uthini ngaye, lokhu evule amehlo akho? Wasesithi: Ungumprofethi\x + 6.14.\x*.
\p
\v 18 AmaJuda-ke kawakholwanga ngaye\x + 9.22. 8.22.\x*, ukuthi wayeyisiphofu usemukele ukubona, aze abiza abazali bakhe osebuye wabona,
\v 19 asebabuza athi: Lo uyindodana yenu, lina elithi yazalwa iyisiphofu yini? Pho isibona njani khathesi?
\v 20 Abazali bakhe bawaphendula bathi: Siyazi ukuthi lo uyindodana yethu, lokuthi wazalwa eyisiphofu;
\v 21 kodwa ukuthi ubona njani khathesi, kasikwazi; kumbe ngubani ovule amehlo akhe, thina kasikwazi; yena usekhulile; mbuzeni, uzazikhulumela yena.
\v 22 Abazali bakhe batsho lezizinto, ngoba besesaba\x + 7.13. Seb. 5.13.\x* amaJuda\x + 9.22. 8.22.\x*; ngoba amaJuda ayesevumelene ngokuthi, uba loba engubani ovuma ukuthi unguKristu\x + 7.45-52.\x*, kakhutshwe esinagogeni\x + 12.42. 16.2. 9.34.\x*.
\v 23 Kungakho abazali bakhe bathi: Usekhulile, mbuzeni.
\p
\v 24 Ambiza-ke ngokwesibili lowomuntu owayeyisiphofu, athi kuye: Phana uNkulunkulu udumo\x + Josh. 7.19.\x*; thina siyazi ukuthi lowomuntu uyisoni\x + 9.16.\x*.
\v 25 Yena wasephendula esithi: Loba eyisoni kangazi, kunye engikwaziyo, ukuthi bengiyisiphofu, khathesi sengibona.
\v 26 Asesithi kuye futhi: Wenzeni kuwe? Uwavule njani amehlo akho?
\v 27 Wawaphendula \add wathi\add*: Sengilitshelile, kodwa kalizwanga\x + 8.43.\x*, lifunelani ukuzwa futhi? Liyafisa lani ukuba ngabafundi bakhe yini?
\v 28 Ngakho amthuka, esithi: Nguwe ongumfundi wakhe; kodwa thina singabafundi bakaMozisi.
\v 29 Thina siyazi ukuthi uNkulunkulu wakhuluma loMozisi; kodwa lo kasimazi lapho avela khona\x + 8.14. 7.27,28.\x*.
\v 30 Umuntu waphendula wathi kuwo: Ngoba kulokhu kuyisimanga ukuthi lina kalimazi lapho avela khona, kanti uvule amehlo ami\x + 3.10.\x*.
\v 31 Njalo siyazi ukuthi uNkulunkulu kazizwa izoni\x + Zaga 1.28. Zaga 28.9.\x*; kodwa uba umuntu engokhonza uNkulunkulu, esenza intando yakhe, uyamuzwa lowo\x + Hlab. 34.15,17. 145.19. Zaga 15.29. Joha. 11.22.\x*.
\v 32 Loba nini kakukaze kuzwakale ukuthi kukhona owavula amehlo owazalwa eyisiphofu\x + Luka 1.70. Seb. 3.21.\x*.
\v 33 Uba lo\x + 9.16. 3.2. 10.21.\x* ubengaveli kuNkulunkulu, ubengebe lamandla okwenza ulutho\x + 6.46.\x*.
\v 34 Aphendula athi kuye: Wena wazalelwa esonweni ngokupheleleyo, njalo wena uyasifundisa yini\x + 13.10. 9.2.\x*? Asemxotshela phandle\x + 12.31.\x*.
\p
\v 35 UJesu wezwa ukuthi amxotshele phandle\x + 12.31.\x*; kwathi esemficile, wathi kuye: Wena uyakholwa yini\x + 1 Joha. 5.13.\x* eNdodaneni kaNkulunkulu\x + 10.36. Mat. 14.33.\x*?
\v 36 Yena waphendula wathi: Ingubani, Nkosi, ukuze ngikholwe kuyo?
\v 37 UJesu wasesithi kuye: Lawe usuyibonile\x + Luka 2.30.\x*, njalo okhuluma lawe uyiyo\x + 4.26.\x*.
\v 38 Wasesithi: Nkosi, ngiyakholwa; wasemkhonza\x + Mat. 8.2.\x*.
\p
\v 39 UJesu wasesithi: Mina ngizele ukwahlulela kulumhlaba, ukuze abangaboniyo babone\x + 5.22,27. 8.26. 3.17. 8.15. 12.47. Luka 2.35.\x*, lalabo ababonayo babe yiziphofu\x + Mat. 9.13. Mark. 2.17. Luka 5.32.\x*.
\v 40 Lalabo kubaFarisi ababelaye bezwa lezizinto, bathi kuye: Lathi siyiziphofu yini\x + Roma 2.19.\x*?
\v 41 UJesu wathi kubo: Uba beliyiziphofu, ngabe kalilasono\x + 15.22,24. Roma 4.15.\x*. Kodwa khathesi lithi: Siyabona; ngakho isono senu simi\x + Roma 2.19.\x*.
